X-WR-CALNAME:Windrush line disruption
BEGIN:VEVENT
DESCRIPTION:<a href="https://tfl.gov.uk/tube-dlr-overground/status/?Input=&lineIds=&dateTypeSelect=Future%20date&direction=&startDate=2026-05-11T05:20:06&endDate=2026-05-11T11:58:33">Disruption map.</a>\n\nWindrush Line: No service between Clapham Junction and Surrey Quays while we fix a signal failure at Denmark Hill. GOOD SERVICE on the rest of the line.  
DTEND:20260511T115833Z
DTSTART:20260511T052006Z
SUMMARY:Windrush line: Part Suspended
UID:8311bc9a-e3fd-49e7-bb34-89b6879e0b0b@8311.org
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
DESCRIPTION:<a href="https://tfl.gov.uk/tube-dlr-overground/status/?Input=&lineIds=&dateTypeSelect=Future%20date&direction=&startDate=2026-05-13T22:30:00&endDate=2026-05-14T00:29:00">Disruption map.</a>\n\nWINDRUSH LINE: Monday 11\, Tuesday 12\, Wednesday 13 and Thursday 14 May\, after 2330 each evening\, no service between New Cross Gate and West Croydon / Crystal Palace after 2330. The 2232 and 2247 trains from Highbury & Islington to West Croydon will both divert to Crystal Palace. The 2338 train from Dalston Junction to New Cross Gate will not run. Last through trains: New Cross Gate to Crystal Palace 2324\, Crystal Palace to New Cross Gate / Highbury & Islington 2332\; New Cross Gate to West Croydon 2330\, West Croydon to New Cross Gate / Highbury & Islington 2316. Rail replacement buses will run as follows: The bus for Crystal Palace will depart London Bridge at 2358 calling at New Cross Gate\, Brockley\, Honor Oak Park\, Forest Hill\, Sydenham\, Crystal Palace\, Gipsy Hill\, West Norwood\, Tulse Hill and Streatham Hill. The bus for East Croydon will depart London Bridge at 0035 calling at New Cross Gate\, Brockley\, Honor Oak Park\, Forest Hill\, Sydenham\, Norwood Junction and East Croydon. One return bus from Crystal Palace departs at 2359\, calling at all stations to London Bridge via New Cross Gate. Alternatively\, use local buses or trams via any reasonable route.
DTEND:20260514T002900Z
DTSTART:20260513T223000Z
SUMMARY:Windrush line: Part Closure
UID:f470def2-b99d-48b0-a242-e54f4930aae9@f470.org
END:VEVENT
