DESCRIPTION:<a href="https://tfl.gov.uk/tube-dlr-overground/status/?Input=&lineIds=&dateTypeSelect=Future%20date&direction=&startDate=2026-05-17T03:30:00&endDate=2026-05-18T00:29:00">Disruption map.</a>\n\nWINDRUSH LINE: Sunday 17 May\, no service between New Cross Gate and West Croydon / Crystal Palace. There will also be no SOUTHERN services between London Bridge and Crystal Palace / Norwood Junction via Forest Hill. Use local London Buses services for Penge West and Anerley\, and connecting Southern services between Crystal Palace\, Norwood Junction and East Croydon. Replacement buses operate between New Cross Gate and Crystal Palace via Brockley\, Honor Oak Park\, Forest Hill and Sydenham.
